> An interactive ML-powered web app that predicts loan default risk from any uploaded dataset — with real-time visualizations, accuracy metrics, and risk verdicts.

---

## 📌 Project Overview

**LoanGuard AI** is a machine learning project built as part of a Classical ML study plan. It uses **Logistic Regression** to predict whether a borrower will default on a loan, and presents the results through a clean **Streamlit web interface**.

Upload any loan dataset CSV → the app auto-trains a model → shows graphs, accuracy metrics, and a risk verdict instantly.

---

## 🎯 Key Features

- 📂 **Upload Any Loan Dataset** — supports Lending Club, Home Credit, German Credit, and more
- 🤖 **Auto-Train Model** — trains Logistic Regression on your data automatically
- 📊 **6 Visualizations** — class distribution, ROC curve, confusion matrix, feature importance, probability distribution, and correlation heatmap
- 🚦 **Risk Verdict** — LOW / MEDIUM / HIGH portfolio risk with percentage score
- 📋 **5 Accuracy Metrics** — Accuracy, AUC-ROC, Precision, Recall, F1 Score
- 👥 **Per-Borrower Predictions** — risk label for every row in your dataset
- 📥 **Download Results** — export all predictions as CSV
- ⚡ **Large Dataset Handling** — auto-samples datasets above 50,000 rows
- 💡 **Knowledge Cards** — ML and finance facts shown during model training
- ⚖️ **Legal Notices** — RBI, DPDPA, and fair lending regulatory information

